<p><b>by 31 January 2012 
</b></p>
<p>12. Communications are sorted in chronological order. Copies of the full text of the communications sent and Government 
replies received may be accessed from the electronic version of this report available on the website of the Human Rights Council. 
Some names of individuals or other information have been rendered anonymous or otherwise unidentifiable. 
</p>
