</p>
<p>Alleged imminent execution of a Mexican national. According to the information received, Mr. 
Humberto Leal Garc&#237;a was scheduled to be put to death in Texas on 7 July 2011. Mr. Garc&#237;a was 
sentenced to death for a murder he committed in 1994 in San Antonio, Texas. Reportedly, at no 
time had he been informed of his right to seek consular assistance as required pursuant to article 
36 of the Vienna Convention on Consular Relations ratified by the United States of America on 
24 November 1969. 
</p>
<p>21/07/2011 
 
 
 
 
 
