Military Intelligences services raided the headquarters of the Assyrian Democratic Organization 
(ADO) in Al-Wusta, Qamishli and arrested 13 activists, without presenting any judicial warrant. 
The agents reportedly returned to ADO&#8223;s headquarters the same day and confiscated computers, 
