Mr. Gabriel Romanos,  Mr. Karam Dawle,  Mr. Samir Ibrahim, Mr. Barsom Yousif, Mr. Gawrieh 
Shabo, Mr. Yaqoub Gharibo, Mr. George Isho, Mr. Ghandi Safar Saado, Mr. Hanna Sanharib 
Shab, Mr. Hanna Ishaq, Mr. Fahad Yousif and Mr. David Habib. On 26 May, they were 
reportedly released without any charges. They had reportedly been detained incommunicado at 
the Political Security branch of Al-Hasakah. Some had allegedly been beaten and insulted by 
State security&#8223;s agents.  
