Razeek was reportedly exhumed and identified. After Mr. Razeek&#8223;s disappearance, individuals 
</p>
<p>campaigning for justice in the case, including his family members, were reportedly subjected to 
harassment and threatened on numerous occasions. In May 2010, members of his family and a 
CTF Trustee received death threats.  
