<p>Alleged abductions on 20 June, 6 August and 5 September 2011 of a human rights defender by 
public officials of the State school and State security agents. According to the information 
received, Mr. Yao Lifa has campaigned for the promotion of political participation through 
monitoring local elections to ensure fairness and transparency, for speaking out against 
corruption in local governance and the electoral processes, and for travelling in the People&#8223;s 
Republic of China to encourage people to run for office as independent candidates. According to 
the source, this year and in 2012, China is holding local People&#8223;s Congress elections and is 
</p>
