<p>Alleged unfair trial and death sentence of mentally ill person. According to the information 
received, Mr. Muhammad Basheer al-Ramaly was convicted of the kidnapping and rape of four 
people in February 2009. He was allegedly sentenced to death by beheading, and subsequent 
crucifixion of his body, by the General Court of Hail. Reportedly, Mr Basheer al-Ramaly is 
mentally ill, he did not enjoy a fair trial, nor did he have access to a lawyer.  
